com.allisonrodenbaugh.springboothelloworld

Class BankAdmin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.allisonrodenbaugh.springboothelloworld.BankAdmin

  • public class BankAdmin
extends java.lang.Object

    Functionality for Bank Administrators

    The BankAdmin class implements the functionality that bank admin select through the controller's UI.

    Note: This class does not take user input directly but simply performs calculations/procedures that the user chose through the UI controller.

    Since:
    Fall 2018
